'''Helen Thomas''' is a [[fugly]] ancient [[old media]] troll who was recently [[Banhammer|forced to retire]] from her job as a long-standing member of the [[Paparazzi|White House Press Corps]] after a video of her sharing her [[Shit nobody cares about|opinions]] about the recent deadly seizure of the [[Freedom Flotilla|Mavi Marmara]] and other ships attempting to pass through an Israeli naval blockade during the [[Jewish Heritage Celebration Day]] media event was widely disseminated via the internet. Thomas is a relic to the golden age of antisemitism and more importantly free speech in America. 

It is a sad day in [[Dumbfuckistan|this country]] when a <s>froggy old hag</s> sweet old lady like Helen Thomas who has been a respected journalist and columnist for [[At least 100 years|over 60 years]] is chased out of office because her views are different from the rest of the pro [[kike|Israel]] media. Showing [[loev|sympathy]] for Palestine in the United States is a crime usually punishable by death, however having a [[Black Jesus|black President]] means that all sentences may be commuted to [[oral sex]] as long as you are a [[fat]] [[white|white]] [[wimminz|woman]].

